Global Rooftop Solar Photovoltaic Installation Market Insights
Rooftop Solar Photovoltaic Installation Market size was valued at USD 50 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 102 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Rooftop Solar Photovoltaic Installation Market Overview
The global rooftop solar photovoltaic (PV) installation market is experiencing significant growth, driven by increasing demand for renewable energy sources and supportive government policies. In 2024, the market was valued at approximately USD 124.42 billion and is projected to reach around USD 534.86 billion by 2034, reflecting a robust compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 15.70% during this period. This expansion is attributed to the growing adoption of solar energy solutions across residential, commercial, and industrial sectors, as well as advancements in solar technology that enhance efficiency and affordability.

